NETWORKING

1. Motivation for using networking
-- Persistency
-- Shared data
-- Using external API's, rich and extensive information

2. Webview
-- Simple way of displaying websites
-- Not what we need if we want to handle the data

3. Network fetching
-- Seperate background thread
-- Runnable task for the thread (FetchJob)
-- Create connection with the server
-- Parse response from server

4. JSON
-- How API's usually serve data
-- Easy to access